LiveSplit layout, splits and autosplitter script for RuneScape 3 Barbarian Assault speedrunning.

Features:
- Works for Normal Mode and Hard Mode
- Starts timer when entering any wave
- Splits when a wave is completed and, if quickstart splits are on, the next wave is started
- Resets when entering wave 1 room (either by leaving wave 1 or reentering through the door) or leaving the BA basement

Setup:
1. Download rs3ba.asl
2. Open LiveSplit
3. In LiveSplit, right-click -> Edit Layout...
4. Click the '+' symbol -> Control -> Scriptable Auto Splitter
5. Double-click Scriptable Auto Splitter to open the settings
6. Browse to and select the rs3ba.asl File
7. Check the settings and click OK